general: Today, the sparkling personalities invite you to emerge from your shell, dear Gemini. The Moon in Pisces forms connections with Uranus, Saturn, and Neptune before moving into Aries, infusing new energy into your social life. With Mars entering Aquarius, your ninth solar house activates, encouraging you to embrace mindfulness and move forward with determination. Remember that every ending opens the door to new beginnings, especially with the union of the Sun and Pluto. It's time to make peace with people or situations that weigh you down. Take advantage of the day to socialize, as Mercury and Venus activate, bringing luck to your friendly and romantic interactions.
love: Dare to express your feelings, love is in the air.
work: Collaborate with those around you to turn your ideas into concrete projects.
health: Take the time to meditate to calm your mind.
teaser: Come out of your shell today!
